  UNRESOLVED RESONANCE REGION : 5.3 EV - 100 KEV                  5247 1451
    THE NEUTRON STRENGTH FUNCTIONS, S0, S1 AND S2 WERE CALCULATED 5247 1451
    WITH OPTICAL MODEL CODE CASTHY/2/.  THE OBSERVED LEVEL SPACING5247 1451
    WAS DETERMINED TO REPRODUCE THE CAPTURE CROSS SECTION         5247 1451
    CALCULATED WITH CASTHY.  THE EFFECTIVE SCATTERING RADIUS WAS  5247 1451
    OBTAINED FROM FITTING TO THE CALCULATED TOTAL CROSS SECTION AT5247 1451
    100 KEV.  THE RADIATION WIDTH GG WAS BASED ON THE SYSTEMATICS 5247 1451
    OF MEASURED VALUES FOR NEIGHBORING NUCLIDES.                  5247 1451
